# Title: Remote Schedule Task Recon via AtScv
# Author: Sagie Dulce, Dekel Paz
# Date: 2022-01-01
# Level: high
# Description: Detects remote RPC calls to read information about scheduled tasks via AtScv
# MITRE Tactic: Discovery
# Tags: attack.discovery
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/application/rpc_firewall/rpc_firewall_atsvc_recon.yml

EventID=3 EventLog="RPCFW" InterfaceUuid="1ff70682-0a51-30e8-076d-740be8cee98b" NOT (OpNum IN (0, 1))